-- noinspection SqlNoDataSourceInspectionForFile



select
    id as customer_id,
    first_name,
    last_name

from raw.jaffle_shop.raw_customers

select
    id as order_id,
    user_id as customer_id,
    order_date,
    status

from raw.jaffle_shop.raw_orders

select
    id,
    order_id,
    payment_method,
    amount

from raw.jaffle_shop.raw_payments

with customers as (

    select * from RAW.JAFFLE_SHOP.stg_customers

),

orders as (

    select * from RAW.JAFFLE_SHOP.stg_orders

),

customer_orders as (

    select
        customer_id,

        min(order_date) as first_order_date,
        max(order_date) as most_recent_order_date,
        count(order_id) as number_of_orders

    from orders

    group by 1

),

final as (

    select
        customers.customer_id,
        customers.first_name,
        customers.last_name,
        customer_orders.first_order_date,
        customer_orders.most_recent_order_date,
        coalesce(customer_orders.number_of_orders, 0) as number_of_orders

    from customers

    left join customer_orders using (customer_id)

)

select * from final

WITH payments AS (
    SELECT p.id AS id,
           p.order_id AS order_id,
           p.payment_method AS payment_method,
           p.amount AS amount,
           o.status AS status
    FROM RAW.JAFFLE_SHOP.stg_payments p
    JOIN RAW.JAFFLE_SHOP.stg_orders o
    ON p.order_id = o.order_id
),
pivoted AS (
    SELECT
        order_id,
        SUM(CASE WHEN payment_method = 'bank_transfer' THEN amount ELSE 0 END) AS bank_transfer_amount,
        SUM(CASE WHEN payment_method = 'coupon' THEN amount ELSE 0 END) AS coupon_amount,
        SUM(CASE WHEN payment_method = 'credit_card' THEN amount ELSE 0 END) AS credit_card_amount,
        SUM(CASE WHEN payment_method = 'gift_card' THEN amount ELSE 0 END) AS gift_card_amount
    FROM payments
    WHERE status = 'completed'
    GROUP BY 1
)

SELECT * FROM pivoted
